          <div class="benefit-card card">
            <h3>Security & Compliance</h3>
            <p>Meet industry standards like SOC 2, HIPAA, GDPR from day one with proper security configurations and audit trails.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-card card">
            <h3>Production-Ready Architecture</h3>
            <p>Scalable, maintainable deployments with high availability, monitoring, and disaster recovery built-in.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-card card">
            <h3>Tailored to Your Needs</h3>
            <p>Custom configurations for your specific use cases, integrations, and performance requirements.</p>
