              <li>Multi-environment setup (dev/staging/prod)</li>
              <li>Production ready cloud deployment</li>
              <li>Load balancing & high availability</li>
              <li>Monitoring & alerting setup</li>
              <li>1 custom integration development</li>
              <li>3 months support</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="package-duration">‚è±Ô∏è 3-4 weeks delivery</div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="package-card card">
            <h3>Enterprise</h3>
            <div class="package-price">Custom</div>
