              <li>Multi-cloud/hybrid deployment</li>
              <li>Custom integrations & APIs</li>
              <li>Compliance assistance (HIPAA, SOC 2, etc.)</li>
              <li>Performance optimization</li>
              <li>Custom monitoring & analytics</li>
              <li>Team training & knowledge transfer</li>
              <li>12 months support</li>
              <li>Dedicated project manager</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="package-duration">‚è±Ô∏è 6-8 weeks delivery</div>
          </div>
